    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PockeDate! – 您的口袋约会模拟器！每次启动都会带来一场全新的约会和独特的对话！与您可爱的、满心爱意的虚拟女友度过无数美好时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >认识一下<strong>Akari</strong> – 您的虚拟甜心，她深深地爱着您。但要小心别让她失望！您可不想看到她难过，对吧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107350/extras/13fddc1b022e2107c60f988eef3e7071.poster.avif?t=1760307898\" width=600 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107350/extras/13fddc1b022e2107c60f988eef3e7071.webm?t=1760307898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107350/extras/13fddc1b022e2107c60f988eef3e7071.mp4?t=1760307898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PockeDate!</strong>不仅仅是一款有趣的游戏，它也是一所约会训练场！通过丰富的互动和独特的情景，您将学会如何更好地沟通，处理尴尬时刻，让您的约会对象感到特别。准备好在与Akari的欢乐时光中提升您的约会技能和信心吧！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色功能：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全免费！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >熟悉的约会场所，每次都有新奇的体验。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱的女孩包容您的所有笨拙！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >温馨、治愈的氛围。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏的约会等待您发现！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精致迷人的像素艺术画风。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原创音乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接您人生中最可爱、最治愈的约会吧，与PockeDate一起享受吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107350/extras/8a39340b579825ef66cd73f7a780711e.poster.avif?t=1760307898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107350/extras/8a39340b579825ef66cd73f7a780711e.webm?t=1760307898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107350/extras/8a39340b579825ef66cd73f7a780711e.mp4?t=1760307898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>PockeDate! - 口袋约会模拟器</i></strong><i>是一款视觉小说，玩家通过阅读文字、做出选择来影响故事的结局。游戏支持自动存档和加载功能。请注意，本游戏无法保证通过经验获得现实中的女友。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107350/extras/1c301e367ff42349db08a3c285ada5ef.poster.avif?t=1760307898\" width=600 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107350/extras/1c301e367ff42349db08a3c285ada5ef.webm?t=1760307898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>尊敬的参与者：</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>您在PockeDate中的体验可能包含令人不安或惊悚的时刻。虽然Akari会努力安慰您，但由于未解决的系统问题，她的状态可能偶尔会变得不稳定。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>请务必小心。这些意外事件是实验的一部分。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>感谢您的参与。</i></p>",
